                                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[Don't Limit Yourself to One Type of Switch on Your Mechanical Keyboard]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/dont-limit-yourself-to-one-type-of-switch-on-your-mechanical-keyboard/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Ismar Hrnjicevic]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/09/img20250922155900-1.jpg" length="3415" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Windows]]></category><category><![CDATA[Mechanical Keyboards]]></category><category><![CDATA[Ajazz AK820]]></category><category><![CDATA[DIY]]></category><category><![CDATA[League of Legends]]></category><description><![CDATA[
                                            Variety is the spice of typing.
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
